{"tid":1592253,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"呢間美容黑店真係核突到...本身係深藍絲，無生意就變黃絲吸引人...大家要小心","createTime":"2019-09-24T13:46:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T16:10:44.000Z","uid":262618,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d2e246cfe9ec795b561d5f4f8fc46d576bdb28e9","tid":1592253,"uid":262618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T13:46:31.000Z","msg":"(睇唔過眼系列)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前有個親戚A係呢間野到做...話個仆街老闆本身係係深藍絲...成日都屌班出去發夢既後生仔，話佢地抵比班黑警打，又話班後生搞到成香港立立亂同埋無生意做。但係佢平時都係靠做大陸客為主既，根本就無諗過香港人對佢地黎講係幾咁重要...<br />\n<br />\n就係今日，仲係果到做既親戚A話今日個老闆見無哂大陸人落黎，生意差左好多，所以就想吸引多D黃絲同埋後生女上去做療程wo..於是就係facebook出左下面呢個post....仆你個街又食義士既人血饅頭...真係好撚核突.....<br />\n<br />\n原POST既LINK: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cutis.HongKong/posts/2434326113269637\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcutis.HongKong%2Fposts%2F2434326113269637&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUtqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=be3d5c59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cutis.HongKong/posts/2434326113269637</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/5lzM1e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5lzM1e5.png&h=d3efe363&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n...仲話與香港共度了不少風雨....話同香港人共同進退，真係你唔講我都笑啦......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係求神拜佛大家唔好再去呢間野到，如果唔係真係對唔住為香港打生打死既義士..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35c09aff7424dbc4a5dacbf650dcf94e7f5b64fc","tid":1592253,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T13:46:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"d7fe198a2c6ccf5887c3208088387c8ae302edcb","tid":1592253,"uid":245409,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T13:50:01.000Z","msg":"其實迫到人扮黃R生意<br />\n<br />\n證明黃影響力其實真係大過藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7618c5e644f6c26070553a1b46261571d310692","tid":1592253,"uid":34714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T13:51:09.000Z","msg":"冇寫到係黃喎"},{"pid":"15f6dbcb154c3af43248f033a17ab582ad0321f0","tid":1592253,"uid":62167,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T13:53:03.000Z","msg":"睇太多咩黃藍店<br />\n所謂證據多數都係片面之詞<br />\n我就直接罷買算數"},{"pid":"4f07917865f989e57e1b40dbb75a07decb580880","tid":1592253,"uid":70973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:20:49.000Z","msg":"[突發]930三罷 文宣工作立即開始!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592295\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592295</a>"},{"pid":"d0fdf05b01698b053dea698c537fa471457ef2dd","tid":1592253,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:38:20.000Z","msg":"乜撚都唔買咪得"},{"pid":"42f6479433b4bfdafb13f520381e16c49727e19e","tid":1592253,"uid":192584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T03:55:29.000Z","msg":"佢有冇支持罷工<br />\n冇就收皮<br />\n8月5個日啊<br />\n共度難關"},{"pid":"858d7e3fe649a86169eb5ce882e7f1a2e2ed4d36","tid":1592253,"uid":262618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42f6479433b4bfdafb13f520381e16c49727e19e","tid":1592253,"uid":192584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T03:55:29.000Z","msg":"佢有冇支持罷工<br />\n冇就收皮<br />\n8月5個日啊<br />\n共度難關"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T14:40:30.000Z","msg":"無 未試過罷工"},{"pid":"5e8a0b8bf36916f612ba72c9df5831ec2538513c","tid":1592253,"uid":308754,"